    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm selling my absolute pride and joy. This car is in incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels just like it did the day it left the showroom. I've babied it since day one, kept it in a climate-controlled garage, and stayed on top of every single service. You won't find a scratch on it! It drives like a dream and is ready for its next adventure. I'm sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to love it. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
