      "description": "Hey there! You have got to see this beauty. It\u2019s honestly an absolute dream\u2014I\u2019ve babied this car from day one and it still feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. It is in truly pristine condition, inside and out, with not a single blemish to be found. I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and I\u2019m looking for someone who will love it just as much as I have. Let's get you behind the wheel for a test drive!",
