    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Offering a museum-quality 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies. This chassis is mechanically flawless, boasting a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory-spec M Variable Differential Lock for precise torque distribution. Comprehensive preventative maintenance has been performed, including a complete VANOS overhaul and structural reinforcement of the rear subframe to eliminate known fatigue points. The suspension retains its original geometry with zero bushing compliance issues, and the engine exhibits a linear power band up to its 8,000 RPM redline. Finished in Carbon Black Metallic with original paint depth and no oxidative wear, this is a rare opportunity for a purist to own a definitive analog performance icon.",
